Title: Jennifer Lopez Love At First Glow Eau de Toilette  -  100 ml(For Women)
Description: Love At First Glow by Jennifer Lopez Perfume. Reminisce about the power of love by wearing Love at First Glow, a youthful and exciting women's fragrance from Jennifer Lopez. Created in 2005, this enticing feminine fragrance lets you unleash your inner superstar. Incredibly glamorous and fun, the scent blends notes of fresh Georgia peach, neroli and Italian bergamot with osmanthus, wild rose, vanilla and musk. Fabulously flirtatious, Love at First Glow attracts attention from the opposite sex and comes packaged in a cute pink bottle. Spray it on to make a stylish statement.

Title: Issey Miyake L'Eau D'Issey Pour Homme Intense Eau de Toilette  -  75 ml(For Men)
Description: Tall, dark and inspiringly handsome, the man who remains grounded to his roots and resembles the heroic protagonist whom novels are woven around, is the man we are talking about. The Issey Miyake L’eau D’issey Pour Homme Intense is a sensuous and provocative fragrance that represents the man of many women’s dreams. Rich and intensely invigorating, this enchanting luxury Eau de Toilette encircles your senses in warm, spicy accords, leaving a trail of mystery and provocation. The opening marks a beautiful, refreshing and citrusy beginning with Mandarin Orange, Yuzu, Sweet Orange, Bergamot and Tangerine. The heart of the fragrance is deep and richly spicy with Nutmeg, Lotus, Cinnamon, Saffron, Cardamom and Camphor, all in the same breath. The final lingering notes are gentle and flirtatiously suggestive with Amber, Papyrus, Benzoin, Incense and Ambergris. With an aura of genuineness and gravity, the Issey Miyake Intense is a luxury Eau de Toilette for the real man.

Burberry Summer for women evokes that peaceful atmosphere of the English summer morning.
